 <name>csDoctrineSlideshowPlugin</name>
 <channel>pear.symfony-project.com</channel>
 <summary>csDoctrineSlideshowPlugin: quickly add slideshows to your project</summary>
 <description>
   csDoctrineSlideshowPlugin allows you to add slides and mix and match with different
   slideshows.  It provides a list of sortable slides for each of your slideshows, and 
   the option to chose different renderers.  Currently, Google Slideshow2 and JQuery Cycle
   are supported.
  </description>
